 managers who know something about DECequipment.andP;  Attepmting to hire these kinds of people, keeping in mind thatthe job will last 18 months to maybe two years, makes recruiting a difficulta difficult process,&quot; Cranford said.andM;In all, more than 600 technical specialists with DEC and other ADPbackgrounds were hired.andM;Cranford said over  the last six months Census telecommunications has beenstable and performed up to expectations.andP;  The hardware has passed all finalchecks, he said.andO;</TEXT></DOC>